{"tid":492600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拖篋採蠔】強國人湧去日本採蠔丟殼 日人憤怒：試過有成100人","createTime":"2017-12-07T16:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T02:41:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de22923538115e0c619cc1b888bc5ca77c640200","tid":492600,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171207/large/1512620453_41fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171207%2Flarge%2F1512620453_41fd.jpg&h=28726241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n流經日本千葉縣市川市的江戶川，數年前開始吸引不少中國人前往採蠔，他們將肉拿走後就將蠔殼隨處丟棄，有礙觀瞻之餘更有不少小孩被蠔殼所傷，令當地人非常頭痛。<br />\n<br />\n「妙典河流環境守護會」會長藤原孝夫表示，該處河流與海水交匯，吸引大量蠔棲息。原本優美的河邊景色，如今卻被堆積如山的蠔殼破壞。被人隨處丟棄的蠔殼，散落在河邊長約1公里的地點，估計有100噸以上。約70名政府職員及當地居民，周一展開清除蠔殼行動，也只是移除了15噸。<br />\n藤原表示，由數年開始前來採蠔的中國人增加，而隨處丟棄蠔殼的問題亦變得嚴重。這些中國人連群結隊，少的有5至10人，多的更有100人以上。藤原說：「這是剝了蠔的殼。只是拿了肉，就把殼丟掉。」他續道：「90%不就是中國人所為嗎？今年8月左右，試過有約100人來（採蠔）。」藤原憤怒地說：「即使叫他們注意，也扮不懂日語不聽人說。」更慘的是不時有小孩子在河邊玩耍時，不慎跌倒就被滿地蠔殼所傷，藤原透露，今是單是救護車也叫了三次。<br />\n有來自中國福建的女子，拖著行李篋前來採蠔，她說：「從朋友口中聽說採到蠔，所以就來了。在家中煮來吃，炸來吃的話很美味。」另一位男子則說：「我是中國來的，採一點蠔，大家一起吃，沒問題。」<br />\n江戸川河川事務所表示，在這兒採蠔並不犯法，只是隨處丟棄蠔殼就是不法棄置。有關方面在該處設置了用日語、韓語、英語及中文簡體字撰寫的告示板，呼籲大家要將蠔殼拿走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171207/57551072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171207%2F57551072&d=W%2Bs0AQgvD%2Bcf6t2x4TcuGkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3b0bbd49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171207%2F57551072&h=f4877113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171207/57551072</a>"},{"pid":"38011f8264bb1816eae05b0d5977a927424eb974","tid":492600,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423441f3f670a43cc9b0b8420423243f1cc74f83","tid":492600,"uid":9348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:48:48.000Z","msg":"黎多劑支那大屠殺殺撚晒班賤畜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e78ad3068edc75aa362775fc94f15e499001cf","tid":492600,"uid":132565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a6e70d24ce319ef08fd865fbe63b0497b1111a","tid":492600,"uid":25086,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎多劑支那大屠殺殺撚晒班賤畜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望到時你屋企人唔係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d3ea55e32e569f1e8f6fdd8d3e479d892a539e","tid":492600,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"係個沙灘落重金屬<br />\n啲蠔食完...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027adeb251fc249662b23292e4a40e9576355ec7","tid":492600,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564d7041afa57578328d9c89061b811f6d79737b","tid":492600,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T17:19: